      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Operation Molot (Hammer)



    Date: May 1981



    Time Limit: 21 turns



    Situation:

    The
    Khost Islamic Liberation Front controls key terrain in the Khost region. Enemy
    forces operate from two fortified strongholds and have garrisoned multiple villages.
    The Khost-Gardez Pass and Ghulam Khan Road are both contested.



    Mission:

    Destroy
    enemy strongholds, liberate occupied villages, and secure both the Khost-Gardez
    Pass and Ghulam Khan Road.



    Enemy Forces:

    Two fortified mountain strongholds
    supported by artillery and anti-aircraft units. Approximately 10 garrison units
    in villages. 5 mobile raiding forces conducting ambush operations.



    Friendly
    Forces:

    Soviet units deploy from Khost. Two airbases provide air support
    and resupply operations.



    Victory Conditions:

    Destroy both enemy strongholds

    Liberate
    all villages

    Secure Khost-Gardez Pass and Ghulam Khan Road'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
